  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>QSimplified</h1>
    <p>A modern, efficient Queue Management System designed for banks, clinics, and service centers.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="qsimplified-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What is QSimplified?</h2>
      <p>QSimplified is Octech’s digital queue management solution that improves customer flow, reduces wait times, and enhances the service experience. It integrates seamlessly with ticket printers, digital signage, and real-time dashboards.</p>

      <h2>Core Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Touchscreen ticket kiosks</li>
        <li>Dynamic display screens</li>
        <li>Staff dashboard & branch control</li>
        <li>SMS notifications</li>
        <li>Daily reports & performance analytics</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Choose QSimplified?</h2>
      <p>Built with simplicity in mind, QSimplified is easy to deploy, cost-effective, and customizable to your service environment.</p>

      <a href="contact.html" class="btn">Request a Demo</a>
    </div>
  </section>

